---
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
---
<Modal modal_id="hitchhiker">
    <main slot="main">

        <h1>The Vanishing Hitchhiker</h1>

        <div style="margin: -20px 0 30px 5px; line-height: 175%;">
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(255,96,66,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">Visual Novel </small>
            &nbsp;
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(255,79,247,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">Nintendo Switch </small>
            &nbsp;
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(111,239,88,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">Released </small>
            &nbsp;
        </div>

        <div class="bannervideo">
            <video style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="auto" controls autoplay muted loop preload="none">
                <source src="/hitchhiker/videos/hitchhiker_banner.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>

        <ol style="margin: 30px 2% 30px 2%; padding-right: 10px; font-size: 1em">
            <p>
                The Vanishing Hitchhiker is a short visual novel for the Nintendo Switch with multiple story paths and endings; and spooky girls.
            </p>
        </ol>
        <ul>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '🗺️ ';">
                The game features multiple choices during the story. These different paths are interconected, resulting in 5 possible endings.
            </li>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '⌨️ ';">
                I created a custom markup language to handle the game's events and branching paths.
            </li>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '🎮 ';">
                The game was released for the Nintendo Switch, and I implemented the Nintendo SDK.
            </li>

        </ul>

        <hr style="border: 1.5px solid #78c2ad; margin-top: 40px">

        <div class="button" style="margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 350%">
            <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/en-gb/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/The-Vanishing-Hitchhiker-2293699.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
               style="margin: 10px;">
                <button class="eshop-button"><nobr><img width="auto" height="28" alt="eshop_logo" style="outline: 0; transform: translateY(17%);" src="/stores/eshop.png"/>&nbsp Nintendo eShop</nobr></button>
            </a>
        </div>

    </main>
</Modal>